snippet.title: Amber Heard restraining order against Johnny Depp   BBC News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has left court in Los Angeles, where she was granted a restraining order against her estranged husband, Johnny Depp.
Depp was ordered to stay 100 yards away from her after Heard claimed that he threw a mobile phone at her on Saturday, hitting her cheek and eye.
The actress filed for divorce on Monday.
